OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain soon
OL,6,Fclearing into the North Sea leading to
OL,7,Fanother hot or exceptionally hot day.
OL,8,FSunny spells and a few showers
OL,9,Fotherwise, mostly in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStill
OL,12,Fvery hot on Saturday, with a chance of
OL,13,Fshowers or thunderstorms. Breezy with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain pushing east on
OL,15,FSunday, cooler. Sunny spells and
OL,16,Fisolated showers on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
